OL,3,CPC charged with terror offences over
OL,4,CWhatsApp messages
OL,6,FA police officer has been charged with
OL,7,Fterrorism offences after allegedly
OL,8,Fsharing messages supporting Hamas.
OL,10,FWest Yorkshire PC Mohammed Adil, 26,
OL,11,Ffaces two counts of publishing an
OL,12,Fimage in support of a proscribed
OL,13,Forganisation.
OL,15,FIt comes after an investigation by
OL,16,FCounter Terrorism Policing North East
OL,17,Finto messages shared on WhatsApp.
OL,19,FThe offences are alleged to have taken
OL,20,Fplace in October and November 2023.
