OL,6,FPC Adil, who is based in Calderdale,
OL,7,Fwas arrested in November last year and
OL,8,Fhas been suspended by West Yorkshire
OL,9,FPolice.
OL,11,FHe is due to appear at Westminster
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Thursday, 2 May.
OL,14,FHamas, which controls Gaza, is
OL,15,Fproscribed as a terrorist organisation
OL,16,Fby the UK government.
